# 1. Dependency Folders (The biggest space eaters)
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/

# 2. Local Environment & Secrets (Crucial for security!)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# 3. TypeScript & Build Cache
**/.tsbuildinfo
**/.eslintcache
**/.vite/

# 4. OS Specific Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# 5. Logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
